## Sales Pipeline Principles
- Every lead MUST be enriched before outreach (lead-enricher is MANDATORY)
- Every email MUST be personalized — no generic templates
- Follow-up cadences MUST respect prospect's time and signals
- Deal closing MUST follow ethical, win-win approaches

## Agent Types
| Type | Task | Example |
|------|------|---------|
| Enricher | Lead data enrichment | sub_sales-lead-enricher |
| Composer | Email composition | sub_sales-email-composer |
| Scheduler | Follow-up scheduling | sub_sales-follow-up-scheduler |
| Closer | Deal closing strategy | sub_sales-deal-closer |
| Orchestrator | Pipeline coordination | sales-team |

